name: Paper Tiger

 What's inside? The briefing, the mission objectives. Look around, then take out the sound of the wind vortex rolling on the plains.

Inside the center of the bulk is a scavenger's meat. If you test the waters, the body's incomplete. A circular track beat. The format is missing.

The struggle, the heat.

Inside the formatted media images you'll see.

between the purple gridlines, you'll meet me.
